parameters.subject: Avoid Projects Delays and Cost Overruns ? [via BNI]
parameters.message:
=Hi {{ $('BNI Data').item.json['Full Name'] }}

Are you worried about delays and cost overruns in your projects?

Construction projects are complex—continuous tracking of labour, materials, and teams is critical to deliver projects on time and within budget. Even a small error can lead to huge losses, theft, or wastage. Do you currently use any software to manage budgets and track sites?

Onsite is designed exclusively for construction projects, letting you track all project elements in one place. Its mobile + web interface enables real-time site tracking and project control.

We’d love to give you a 10-minute demo of the software. How about tomorrow evening?

Just reply “YES”, and I’ll set up a convenient time.

Warm regards,
Akshansh Agarwal
Cofounder & CEO
BNI Member (Acheivers, Noida)

=Hi {{ $('BNI Data').item.json['Full Name'] }}

Cost overruns are the biggest challenge in any construction project—and often, nobody knows why the costs increased.

That’s why we built Onsite: a software platform designed to solve real on-ground challenges across every stage of a project. With Onsite, you can do budgeting, planning, and tracking of labour, materials, and progress—all in one place.

Would you be open to a quick 10-minute chat to see how we’re helping 2,000+ companies stay on time and on budget?

Just reply “YES”, and I’ll schedule a convenient time.

Warm regards,
Akshansh Agarwal
Cofounder & CEO
BNI Member (Acheivers, Noida)

=Hi {{ $json['Full Name'] }}

There are countless ways projects lose money—but only one proven way to save: deeper control.

Onsite helps you achieve exactly that—reducing theft, cutting wastage, and enabling smarter negotiations, driving savings at every stage of your project.
